    "posts": [
      {
        "id": 255503,
        "name": "Jeremy",
        "username": "jeremysee",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/jeremysee/{size}/49574_2.png",
        "created_at": "2024-11-13T23:43:46.775Z",
        "cooked": "<p><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/1/b/1bf4b8ca93cbf9b0604a480419a273e779e95d20.png\" alt=\"signal1\" data-base62-sha1=\"3ZjcLcHDbjQL45PTDP9OMbFcGf6\" width=\"337\" height=\"136\"></p>\n<p>In the latest desktop app, the unread messages badge visually dominates the system tray / notification area icon so much that the Signal icon just looks like a big red 3 at a glance. What app is that again?</p>\n<p>I just noticed this problem. I’m not sure if that’s just because they recently changed the icon colour and the deeper blue doesn’t stand out as much against black, or whether they made other changes - enlarged the badge or changed the tray icon a bit.</p>\n<p>In any case, a badge that obscures ~75% of the actual icon and renders it illegible at a glance is bad. A couple of icons over you can see an example of a tray icon with a badge that does not render the actual icon illegible.</p>\n<p>There’s various ways of fixing this problem (enlarge icon, reduce badge, make other changes to icon) and I don’t really have a preference among them.</p>\n<p>Here’s the icon/badge in the context of a Windows 10 desktop at 1920x1080:<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/d/2d7a88ec20172e322412932f7fcbadb02e984855.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/2d7a88ec20172e322412932f7fcbadb02e984855\" title=\"signal2\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/d/2d7a88ec20172e322412932f7fcbadb02e984855_2_690x388.jpeg\" alt=\"signal2\" data-base62-sha1=\"6uk0Z37950H7Cez9p9QjZMygIhD\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/d/2d7a88ec20172e322412932f7fcbadb02e984855_2_690x388.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/d/2d7a88ec20172e322412932f7fcbadb02e984855_2_1035x582.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/d/2d7a88ec20172e322412932f7fcbadb02e984855_2_1380x776.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"C5C9CA\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">signal2</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×1080 193 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
